<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" identifier="Q22_v7" title="Q22_v7" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>En la ficha de una cuenta de una red social se registra el siguiente desglose sobre una campaña publicitaria:<br />- Seguidores al inicio de la campaña: 2 000 000<br />- Nuevos seguidores ganados durante la campaña (respecto del inicio): 50 000</p>
    <p>¿Qué porcentaje de aumento en seguidores representó la campaña con respecto a la cantidad inicial de seguidores?</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">2 %<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. El porcentaje de aumento se calcula como <m:math display="inline"><m:mrow><m:mn>50&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>2&#160;000&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0,025</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, y <m:math display="inline"><m:mrow><m:mn>0,025</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>100</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2,5</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math>. Por lo tanto, <m:math display="inline"><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> no corresponde al aumento indicado.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">2,5 %<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! El aumento porcentual respecto de la cantidad inicial es <m:math display="inline"><m:mrow><m:mn>50&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>2&#160;000&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0,025</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Al multiplicar por <m:math display="inline"><m:mrow><m:mn>100</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, se obtiene <m:math display="inline"><m:mrow><m:mn>2,5</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math>. Por eso, la campaña representó un aumento de <m:math display="inline"><m:mrow><m:mn>2,5</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">25 %<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. El cálculo correcto es <m:math display="inline"><m:mrow><m:mn>50&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>2&#160;000&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0,025</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Luego, <m:math display="inline"><m:mrow><m:mn>0,025</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>100</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2,5</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math>. La opción <m:math display="inline"><m:mrow><m:mn>25</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> sería diez veces mayor que el porcentaje real.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">50 %<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si el aumento fuera <m:math display="inline"><m:mrow><m:mn>50</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math>, entonces debería ser la mitad de <m:math display="inline"><m:mrow><m:mn>2&#160;000&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, es decir, <m:math display="inline"><m:mrow><m:mn>1&#160;000&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> seguidores. Pero el aumento real fue <m:math display="inline"><m:mrow><m:mn>50&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> seguidores, y <m:math display="inline"><m:mrow><m:mn>50&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>2&#160;000&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0,025</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, que equivale a <m:math display="inline"><m:mrow><m:mn>2,5</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Identificar los datos del problema</strong></p>
            <p>Cantidad inicial de seguidores: <m:math display="inline"><m:mrow><m:mn>2&#160;000&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>.</p>
            <p>Aumento de seguidores durante la campaña: <m:math display="inline"><m:mrow><m:mn>50&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Usar la fórmula de porcentaje de aumento respecto del valor inicial</strong></p>
            <p><m:math display="inline"><m:mrow><m:mi>Porcentaje&#160;de&#160;aumento</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mi>aumento</m:mi><m:mi>cantidad&#160;inicial</m:mi></m:mfrac><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>100</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Reemplazar por los valores del enunciado</strong></p>
            <p><m:math display="inline"><m:mrow><m:mi>Porcentaje&#160;de&#160;aumento</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>50&#160;000</m:mn><m:mn>2&#160;000&#160;000</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>100</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Calcular la división</strong></p>
            <p><m:math display="inline"><m:mrow><m:mn>50&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>2&#160;000&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0,025</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Convertir a porcentaje</strong></p>
            <p><m:math display="inline"><m:mrow><m:mn>0,025</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>100</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2,5</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>.</p>
            <p>Entonces, el aumento fue de <m:math display="inline"><m:mrow><m:mn>2,5</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La campaña publicitaria representó un aumento de <m:math display="inline"><m:mrow><m:mn>2,5</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> con respecto a la cantidad inicial de seguidores.</p>
            <p>La alternativa correcta es la B.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>